title: A silly Vayne Video! Yeet.

body: I swear I used to be good at her a couple of seasons ago :/ {{item:3070}}

replies.body: Yeet is a celebratory term used in the same sense as the words "fantastic" or "awesome" with the slight variation of being used in a 'internet meme' context
